y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解個世界要咁殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b89d9240b7fc10f8a095beeff4ce4e41a67a0b","tid":179064,"uid":25494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:45:36.000Z","msg":"拍拖呢d做仲係學生 玩下就好<br />\n出到黎社會？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ede6a40bce194545839fb6ffbf914db6f4aff20","tid":179064,"uid":93484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無能力 都可以努力d嫁 巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢排諗緊進修同考返個車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考左冇錢養車都係冇用<br />\n<br />\n1 2 3 22 牌已有, 但冇車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗住考定有時去旅行可以自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae96e8435d2fea6103ef0f98d05b23e649eec572","tid":179064,"uid":93484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵個同自己水平差唔多咪得law.<br />\n兩個人生活易過一個人.</blockquote><br />\n但我發現我呢d小毒L識女仔好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想搵到都差不多水平的仲難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc7f7b1ef06ce54f2d055027a9d2ce8c514564f","tid":179064,"uid":93484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍拖呢d做仲係學生 玩下就好<br />\n出到黎社會？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能係我大個左被同化<br />\n我成日會諗兩個人起埋一齊需要一個原因<br />\n你對佢一見鍾情又好 你想同佢扑野又好 你想保護佢照顧佢又好 你鍾意佢d名利地位錢都好 <br />\n但我比較想搵一個大家對對方有感覺而又可以互相為大家付出的人真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n哼著: 仍然沒有 遇到 那位跟我絕配的戀人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3073450910acbf27709c9d1946127221ecc4cd","tid":179064,"uid":35888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>物質不代表幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"91b226e037de6d2fe5a1ee31f1846606ddc72019","tid":179064,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:13:41.000Z","msg":"唉。。 我最後都係忍唔住。。勉強幸福"},{"pid":"7c206631df355ca690441678ef6518280520506d","tid":179064,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:27:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係好驚害左人，但明明唔係窮、冇潛力或者對佢唔好，咁都帽事，我真係驚自己有乜大缺陷係身邊冇人睇到或者係睇到唔同我講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打單身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n被帽事左仲要放棄左，依家單身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉我諗起一年前第一次拍拖個女仔就一腳踏兩船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解個世界要咁殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都唔知點講好，有興趣又有時間既既起我底睇下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{